E_D("replace into `article` values('17','0','如何去除茶杯上的茶垢？','<p> <strong><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 0, 0); font-family: tahoma, arial, 宋体; font-size: 14px; line-height: 25px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">以下介绍几种除茶垢的方法： </span></strong><span style=\"color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: tahoma, arial, 宋体; font-size: 14px; line-height: 25px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\"> </span><br style=\"color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: tahoma, arial, 宋体; font-size: 14px; line-height: 25px; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\"><span style=\"color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: tahoma, arial, 宋体; font-size: 14px; line-height: 25px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">（1）除掉金属制的茶<span style=\"color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: tahoma, arial, 宋体; font-size: 14px; line-height: 25px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">壶</span>上的茶垢，使用金属制的茶隔时，会因茶垢而变得乌黑，如用中型清洁剂也洗不掉的，可用醋浸泡，或用漂白剂浸泡后可轻易去垢。  </span></p>\n<p><span style=\"color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: tahoma, arial, 宋体; font-size: 14px; line-height: 25px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\"><img src=\"http://static.i3.xywy.com/cms/20150205/36df98ed6fa826c8379373fe2f7c548b59713.jpg\"></span></p>\n<p><span style=\"color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: tahoma, arial, 宋体; font-size: 14px; line-height: 25px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">（2）除掉茶杯或茶壶上的茶垢，茶杯、茶壶用久了，就会由大量茶垢，用海绵蘸盐磨擦，可轻易去掉。 </span><br style=\"color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: tahoma, arial, 宋体; font-size: 14px; line-height: 25px; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\"></p>\n<p><span style=\"color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: tahoma, arial, 宋体; font-size: 14px; line-height: 25px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\"><img src=\"http://imgqn.koudaitong.com/upload_files/2015/07/15/Fnf_xab6GrCbXho7mO4XEV56kvfJ.jpg!730x0.jpg\"></span></p>\n<p><span style=\"color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: tahoma, arial, 宋体; font-size: 14px; line-height: 25px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">（3）除小块茶垢，可将其浸泡于漂白剂或清洁粉的溶液中，并放置一晚，就可去掉茶垢。 </span></p>\n<p><span style=\"color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: tahoma, arial, 宋体; font-size: 14px; line-height: 25px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\"><img src=\"http://pic.baike.soso.com/p/20140429/20140429144237-1981842174.jpg\"> </span></p>\n<p><span style=\"color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: tahoma, arial, 宋体; font-size: 14px; line-height: 25px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">（4） 可用牙膏或打碎的鸡蛋壳擦洗, 再用清水冲净即可。  </span></p>\n<p><span style=\"color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: tahoma, arial, 宋体; font-size: 14px; line-height: 25px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\"><img src=\"http://image.nbd.com.cn/uploads/articles/thumbnails/24648/111.x_large.jpg\"></span></p>\n<p><span style=\"color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: tahoma, arial, 宋体; font-size: 14px; line-height: 25px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">       喝茶的好处众所周知，然而很多老年人的茶杯却泛黄发黑，积攒下一层厚厚的茶垢，如不及时洗，经常用这样的茶杯喝茶，会引起人的早衰。喝茶聊天是人生一大享受。然而有人茶杯里总积一层厚厚的茶垢，甚至以为有茶垢的茶具冲泡出来的茶更有味。殊不知，茶垢对人体健康是极为不利的。  </span></p>\n<img src=\"http://tj.koudaitong.com/1.gif?spm=m1436950328399215434014333.sendall_mp623025&amp;fm=display&amp;time=1436950328&amp;kdt_id=801320\">','[weixin]http://mmbiz.qpic.cn/mmbiz/ybgpOp5vGcK6IelS3oWubH76mLnLjgWB9jicPVs8D6LIrria5WianvSE7tVuQwW9EJGPDBHw6BgU8cLWnTVKfdgtg/0?wx_fmt=jpeg','34','27','-1','0.05','2015-08-02');");
E_D("replace into `article` values('18','0','这样的男人，让他滚！','<p style=\"\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;\">当你胃疼、或是每月那几天来的时候肚子疼，你和他说：亲爱的，我疼。如果他说：那吃点药吧，我也没办法啊。</span></p>\n<p style=\"\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;\">那么，离开他，他不爱你，所以不会在乎你有多难受，不会懂得心疼你。</span></p>\n<p style=\"\"><img src=\"http://mmbiz.qpic.cn/mmbiz/57UkybnAqpo2bxiclbicoX6CaziaBTZc5bQ5jJlyyqDceWNuIaibvMMrff2Ls4WBzbbibeLrxAqBPicmy41qCjuoxf6Q/0?wx_fmt=png\" data-s=\"300,640\" data-ratio=\"0.8850267379679144\" data-w=\"374\" data-type=\"png\" width=\"auto\" style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important; visibility: visible !important; width: auto !important;\"><br style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;\"></p>\n<p style=\"\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;\">当你们吵架的时候，他不找你，只是放你一个人苦苦等待，而他和往常一样吃喝玩乐。</span></p>\n<p style=\"\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;\">那么，离开他，他不在乎你的感受。所以更不要奢望他会心疼你，那不可能。</span></p>\n<p style=\"\"><img src=\"http://mmbiz.qpic.cn/mmbiz/57UkybnAqpo2bxiclbicoX6CaziaBTZc5bQ2vjMbkWkw0JRN46kWOoKvoicaD08ryncQnJbLCzI2nPiaBictVrPFwKYg/0?wx_fmt=jpeg\" data-s=\"300,640\" data-ratio=\"0.712166172106825\" data-w=\"337\" data-type=\"jpeg\" width=\"auto\" style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important; visibility: visible !important; width: auto !important;\"><br style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;\"></p>\n<p style=\"\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;\">当你因为其他的事情悲伤难过希望他安慰的时候，他不管不问。还说：我理解不了你的想法，有什么可难受的。</span></p>\n<p style=\"\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;\">那么，离开他，你的生活，你的一切对于他来说都是无所谓的。</span></p>\n<p style=\"\"><img src=\"http://mmbiz.qpic.cn/mmbiz/57UkybnAqpoqSOUbWpBy5UVhGNMdyUkBiazGLibCglVlO7QTEdW2rthDq7KTDYpfM8AcJkTmVSVxuFsObnKzmRVA/0?wx_fmt=jpeg\" data-s=\"300,640\" data-ratio=\"0.662\" data-w=\"500\" data-type=\"jpeg\" width=\"auto\" style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important; visibility: visible !important; width: auto !important;\"><br style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;\"></p>\n<p style=\"\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;\">如果他经常骗你。</span></p>\n<p style=\"\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; line-height: 1.5em; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;\">那么，离开他，真正爱你的人是不经常对你撒谎的，他骗你，是因为不够重视你。</span></p>\n<p style=\"\"><img src=\"http://mmbiz.qpic.cn/mmbiz/57UkybnAqpoqSOUbWpBy5UVhGNMdyUkBhnmsEULeTrQG90CwQRWFpeVL8Eqw1efEYJux2C5ZROiadM7xT6HOwng/0?wx_fmt=png\" data-s=\"300,640\" data-ratio=\"0.6600397614314115\" data-w=\"\" data-type=\"png\" width=\"auto\" style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important; visibility: visible !important; width: auto !important;\"><br style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;\"></p>\n<p style=\"\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;\">如果他说：我不是个懂浪漫的人，所以，我不记得你生日、我们的纪念日。</span></p>\n<p style=\"\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;\">那么，离开他，你还有什么可以留恋，他只是在为他不爱你找借口。</span></p>\n<p style=\"\"><img src=\"http://mmbiz.qpic.cn/mmbiz/57UkybnAqpoqSOUbWpBy5UVhGNMdyUkB9zyQZbZcm0H8fAJNAsZf508DXsUrRDexHBkJbOpRv2sgBiaBFxfjpYg/0?wx_fmt=jpeg\" data-s=\"300,640\" data-ratio=\"0.6003976143141153\" data-w=\"\" data-type=\"jpeg\" width=\"auto\" style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important; visibility: visible !important; width: auto !important;\"><br style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;\"></p>\n<p style=\"\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;\">如果你和朋友在一起吃饭或一起游玩的时候，他一脸的烦躁和无奈。</span></p>\n<p style=\"\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;\">那么，离开他，真正爱你的人，会给足你面子，他会让所有人都知道你是幸福的。</span></p>\n<p style=\"\"><img src=\"http://mmbiz.qpic.cn/mmbiz/57UkybnAqpp3tABBm2EgrhGtod2tc1UxHZZias4GLkgcOdjJI5a0NRIFtCTPspuq25yGlPtpJvKicOge6CQT1gTA/0?wx_fmt=png\" data-s=\"300,640\" data-ratio=\"0.8877005347593583\" data-w=\"374\" data-type=\"png\" width=\"auto\" style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important; visibility: visible !important; width: auto !important;\"><br style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;\"></p>\n<p style=\"\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;\">如果当你开心的时候，你找他一起分享快乐，他很心不在焉，不爱听你说话。</span></p>\n<p style=\"\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;\">那么，离开他，真正