;\"><strong style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;\"></strong></span></p>\n<fieldset class=\"135editor\" data-id=\"27\" style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; min-width: 0px; border: 0px currentcolor; color: rgb(37, 37, 37); line-height: 24.44px; font-family: 微软雅黑; font-size: 14.44px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;\"><p class=\"135brush\" data-brushtype=\"text\" style=\"margin-top: -1px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; min-height: 30px; white-space: pre-wrap; border-color: rgb(218, 137, 133); border-top-left-radius: 3px; border-top-right-radius: 3px; border-bottom-right-radius: 3px; border-bottom-left-radius: 3px; height: 30px; text-align: center; color: rgb(255, 255, 255); line-height: 30px; font-weight: bold; visibility: visible; orphans: 2; widows: 2; box-shadow: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.14902) 1px 1px 3px; background-color: rgb(216, 40, 33); box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; line-height: 24.44px; font-size: 18px; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;\">这个太重要了，告诉朋友，也许他们也需要！</span></p></fieldset></section></section></section><p>【文章改编自网络，如有侵权请联系删除】</p>','[weixin]http://mmbiz.qpic.cn/mmbiz/w3mcYJzia3H8HR5sYdMMA5wT77Z4vRRzkh8zdLKZWAc4kW4t5RQ1SEfU0VxGIktFO7yAYYANia5B0PoWqlQMFekA/0?wx_fmt=jpeg','34','17','-1','0.05','2015-08-02');");
